description.narrative: Thanks to UNICEF support, in 2021 the Ministry of Health and the Ministry of Education officially committed to promote and support actively Birth registration, with the launch of two strategic national guidelines, one for the establishment of civil registry support desks within health facilities, the other for systematic detection and registration of students without birth certificates. More evidence is also available to support BR programming, with a study on the socio-cultural determinants of non-civil registration and a KAP study on birth registration. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:03/02/2022
